write_lec_dire...y_naming_style(25.10)  write_lec_dire...y_naming_style(25.10)

Name
       write_lec_directory_naming_style

Syntax
        write_lec_directory_naming_style <directory_name>

       Type: String

       Default: fv/invs/%s

       Specifies  the directory name where the write_do_lec command will write
       verification files when the write_lec_files global is true. The  direc-
       tory  will  be  created if it does not already exist, and will be over-
       written if the existing directory has the same name. A %s in the string
       is replaced with the design name. For example, it  will  overwrite  the
       directory  for  the same design but not for a different design. A %d in
       the string is replaced with a unique integer to avoid  overwriting  any
       existing directory.

Related Information
              * write_do_lec

              * write_lec_files

